{"tid":2272862,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男子止痛藥企圖餵狗　企圖殘害動物罪成判監獲緩刑","createTime":"2020-11-05T10:29:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T10:29:45.000Z","uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3c313bb912545e98820fcfb5a0b6bfcff773fd0e","tid":2272862,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T10:29:45.000Z","msg":"一名69歲男子因不滿鄰居的狗隻過於嘈吵，涉嫌於去年11月20日將止痛藥物「克痛」藏於芝士腸中，企圖餵食鄰居所養的狗隻，在東區裁判法院被裁定一項「企圖殘害動物罪」罪成，判監禁4星期，緩刑18個月。<br />\n<br />\n全文:<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558552-20201105.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558552-20201105.htm&d=GnUrxgUttZjT4wJVsekm4H%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=ad0f77dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558552-20201105.htm&h=64d53126\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558552-20201105.htm</a>"}]}